,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:09:59.000Z","msg":"點解搓手液係用甲醇？甲醇連搓手都會中毒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我唔敢用商場啲搓手液就係咁解，都唔知啲垃圾物業管理識唔識買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8b3ee4a1c89f6388c1dcc3a0925d76d49fc2c3","tid":2299003,"uid":268342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:16:55.000Z","msg":"飲飲下可能進化到呢，唔好限制人既能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}